      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IDYLLIC JAMES (3) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and four minors from eight tries. Recorded a one length win (24.01) in a Special conditions Veteran race last time at Bendigo. Rates on top and should go close. WEBLEC BILLY (2) isn't a quick beginner but comes home hard, finishing out of the frame two back but did wind up strongly to place when third (19.50) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Expected to feature. GOLD CLASS COOL (1) is mixing form and out of the placings last time but was a Grade 5 winner three starts ago and moves to Box 1 this time where he has performed well. Expected to do much better this time. SONIC DIESEL (8) is worth including after a top-three finish at this track and distance most recently.",
